Purpose in Hackathon

This module demonstrates:

Real-time disaster prediction

Automated alert generation

High-frequency hourly forecasting

Multi-variable hazard fusion


It adds a strong risk management and urgent-response capability to the AetherVision Omega system, showcasing strong AI and Smart City domain knowledge.


